0fb4			;                pop     af 
0fb4			;                ret 
0fb4			; 
0fb4			; Get a byte in hexadecimal notation. The result is returned in A. Since 
0fb4			; the routine get_nibble is used only valid characters are accepted - the  
0fb4			; input routine only accepts characters 0-9a-f. 
